race.comment: ROCK THE SUNRISE (8) is an honest commodity who has only missed the top-five once in ten career starts and doesn't know how to put in a poor one. Gets the services of Wiggins on board from the inside marble and can run a big race while fresh. CERTIFIED COPY (6) boasts a win around this circuit and will find this easier than the recent Saturday metro placing last time out. Include in calculations. HEAVENLY IMPACT (2) saves his best form for his home circuit here and will be rock-hard fit for this. Top-three prospects. HERMIONE PRANCER (18) broke the maiden status at the latest effort and will have taken some confidence from that breakthrough victory. Can go back-to-back. LET'S DO IT AGAIN (10) best of the rest with the claim.
